Two Big Brother Naija Season seven housemates, Groovy and Beauty have been flirting with each other. The pair seemed to have formed a connection already on Day two of the show. It all started when the ‘Level 2 Housemates’ decided to play a game of ‘Truth or Dare’. During the game, Beauty was dared to kiss Groovy but he refused, leaving Beauty feeling slighted.   #BBNaija – Ebuka speaks on Groovy’s alleged bad…     Three popular female celebrities vying for political offices     Davido declares dad ‘GOAT’   “I feel like it’s a bit too early for this,” he said. Continuing Groovy said: “If I am out of the picture, would it not be easier for you to do what you’re here to do?”. In her response, Beauty complained that Groovy was being uptight as she left the game. “I can be cranky for other things but not this. This whole process is a lot for me,” she said.